ZH: 我们都应该谴责暴力行为。
EN: We should all condemn acts of violence.

ZH: 这个组织谴责政府的不公正行为。
EN: This organization condemns the government's unfair actions.

ZH: 谴责种族主义是我们的责任。
EN: It is our responsibility to condemn racism.

ZH: 杂志刊登了一篇谴责腐败的文章。
EN: The magazine published an article condemning corruption.

ZH: 他们公开谴责了他的行为。
EN: They openly condemned his actions.

ZH: 这位演员因为其言论遭到谴责。
EN: The actor was condemned for his statements.

ZH: 我们不能对违法行为保持沉默，我们必须谴责。
EN: We cannot remain silent about illegal actions, we must condemn.

ZH: 他的偷窃行为应该受到大家的谴责。
EN: His theft should be condemned by everyone.

ZH: 这一行为受到了世界各地媒体的一致谴责。
EN: This action has been unanimously condemned by media around the world.

ZH: 我们决不能容忍和谴责歧视行为。
EN: We must never tolerate and condemn acts of discrimination.

ZH: 这项提案遭到了各方面的广泛谴责。
EN: This proposal has been widely condemned by all parties.

ZH: 谴责并不会解决问题，我们需要采取实际行动。
EN: Condemnation will not solve the problem, we need to take practical actions.

ZH: 谴责他并不能改变事实的发生。
EN: Condemning him will not change the fact that it happened.

ZH: 我们强烈谴责他的不负责任行为。
EN: We strongly condemn his irresponsible behavior.

ZH: 这次事件引发了公众的谴责和愤怒。
EN: This incident has provoked public condemnation and anger.

ZH: 谴责需要众人的力量来实现正义。
EN: Condemnation requires the power of the people to achieve justice.

ZH: 我们对这种行为表示谴责并保留采取法律行动的权利。
EN: We condemn this behavior and reserve the right to take legal action.

ZH: 他的言论引起了社会的广泛谴责。
EN: His statements have sparked widespread social condemnation.

ZH: 谴责他是唯一正确的选择。
EN: Condemning him is the only right choice.

ZH: 媒体对这起丑闻发表了一篇谴责文章。
EN: The media published a condemning article about the scandal.
